{"tid":601703,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"中石油去年盈利升近兩倍","createTime":"2018-03-22T12:04:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-23T05:05:23.000Z","uid":70274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d31e1ecb0a879d071ecaf741a305b241c735ec43","tid":601703,"uid":70274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T12:04:30.000Z","msg":"香港電台-財經<br />\n<br />\n中石油去年盈利227.98億元人民幣，按年急升1.9倍，派末期息每股2.489分人民幣，及特別息3.585分人民幣，合共每股派息6.074分人民幣。<br />\n期內，營業額20159億元，按年升24.7%。油氣產量微跌0.6%至14.58億桶油當量，原油銷量增加14.8%至1.15億噸，平均實現油價上升27.2%至每噸2392元。集團期內加工原油 10.17億桶，增長6.7%。<br />\n【獨家：泰國三大發展商AP - 名牌大學旁的雙鐵零接觸價細樓】<br />\nSponsored Globalhome 海外買家<br />\n另外，去年資本開支2162億元，集團預計今年資本開支為2258億元，按年增加4.4%。"},{"pid":"0cf8041412e42ab5018147b8bf915e58eca11d32","tid":601703,"uid":124037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T12:14:32.000Z","msg":"2318 175 700 3888<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"743030b8de3a5dee1909db2e3c9294652e4c4bf4","tid":601703,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T12:16:10.000Z","msg":"okay 沽埋你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b9ef263515df10596dc6c08df5f358286b8db33","tid":601703,"uid":87672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T12:19:25.000Z","msg":"咁仲唔係時候比人出貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9337d4ff9db8bde7c0011f1906e9c4ad05ff237c","tid":601703,"uid":56752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T12:42:38.000Z","msg":"all in call<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44c3406b35255d0a5cb2cda6c7c563fd458cdb82","tid":601703,"uid":118571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T02:46:36.000Z","msg":"屌，咁都唔撚升"},{"pid":"53560dbdb2b25ee7eec8a38d2c61d8c6ac97172d","tid":601703,"uid":166082,"like":0